Package: libquill-logger-dev
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         ${shlibs:Depends},
         libquill-dev,
         ros-humble-rclcpp-dev,
         ros-humble-rcl-dev,
         ros-humble-rcutils-dev,
         ros-humble-rosidl-runtime-c-dev
Description: High-performance ROS2 logging system using Quill library
 This package provides a high-performance ROS2 logging system based on the Quill library.
 It can be used as a drop-in replacement for the default ROS2 logger with improved
 performance and realtime capabilities.
 .
 Features:
  - Asynchronous logging with minimal overhead
  - Configurable output formats
  - Realtime performance optimizations
  - Full ROS2 logging API compatibility
  - Thread-safe implementation

Package: quill-logger-demo
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         ${shlibs:Depends},
         libquill-logger-dev,
         ros-humble-rclcpp
Description: Demo applications for quill-logger
 This package contains demonstration applications and examples for the quill-logger
 library, including test nodes and usage examples.

Package: quill-logger-dbg
Architecture: any
Section: debug
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         libquill-logger-dev (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Debug symbols for quill-logger
 This package contains debug symbols for the quill-logger library. 